Completed Task :- 
Display a list of products on the homepage, with pagination and a search bar to filter products by name.
Allow users to create new products by filling out a form with fields for name, description, price, and image (using Laravel's built-in image uploading functionality).
Allow users to edit and delete existing products by clicking on a product from the homepage and navigating to a separate edit page.


Technical Requirements:
Use Laravel's validation system to ensure data inputted by the user is valid (e.g. product name is required, price is a number, etc.).


